Installation Guide/gitcode.title: GitHub Codespaces
Installation Guide/gitcode.description: 1. Open the SuperAGI GitHub repository https://github.com/TransformerOptimus/SuperAGI/ and click on Code > Codespaces > Create new codespace

Installation Guide/local.title: Win/MacOS/Linux
Installation Guide/local.description: 1. Download the repo using git clone https://github.com/TransformerOptimus/SuperAGI.git in your terminal or directly from github page in zip format.

superagi-home.title: Introduction to SuperAGI
superagi-home.description: A dev-first open source autonomous AI agent framework. Enabling developers to build, manage & run useful autonomous agents quickly and reliably.

Toolkit/coding_tool.title: Coding Tool
Toolkit/coding_tool.description: The robust SuperAGI Coding Tool lets help with their coding tasks like writing, reviewing, refactoring code, fixing bugs, and understanding programming concepts.

Toolkit/email.title: Email Tool
Toolkit/email.description: The robust SuperAGI Email Tool lets users send and read emails while providing a foundation for other fascinating use cases.

Toolkit/github.title: GitHub Tool
Toolkit/github.description: The SuperAGI GitHub Tool enables users to perform various operations on GitHub repositories which include adding files or folders, deleting files, and searching for files or folders within a repository.

Toolkit/google_search.title: Google Search Tool
Toolkit/google_search.description: The SuperAGI Google Search Tool helps users perform a Google search and extract snippets and webpages.

Toolkit/google_serp.title: Google SERP Search Tool
Toolkit/google_serp.description: The SuperAGI Google Search Tool helps users perform a Google search and extract snippets and webpages.

Toolkit/Image Generation Toolkit/dalle.title: Dall-E Tool
Toolkit/Image Generation Toolkit/dalle.description: The SuperAGI Image Generation Tool helps you generate an image with a prompt using DALL-E.

Toolkit/Image Generation Toolkit/stable_.title: Stable Diffusion Tool
Toolkit/Image Generation Toolkit/stable_.description: Introducing Stable Diffusion Integration with SuperAGI

Toolkit/jira.title: Jira Tool
Toolkit/jira.description: The SuperAGI Jira Tool lets users create, edit and search issues while providing a foundation for other great use cases.

Toolkit/searx.title: Searx Search Tool
Toolkit/searx.description: The SuperAGI Searx Search Tool helps users perform a Searx search and extract snippets and webpages. We parse the HTML response pages because most Searx instances do not support the JSON response format without an API key.

Toolkit/slack.title: Slack Toolkit
Toolkit/slack.description: This SuperAGI Tool lets users send messages to Slack Channels and provides a strong foundation for use cases to come.

Toolkit/webscraper.title: Web Scraper Tool
Toolkit/webscraper.description: The SuperAGI Webscraper Tool lets users perform web scraping, extracting URLs and retrieving the textual content from websites.
